divs: Sighting DetailsIm in NW Austin at the Arboretum, looking to the east there is a circular pattern of very bright lights seemingly circulating around an object high up in the sky. I thought maybe it was coming from the ground, like a car dealership with a couple huge spotlights, but the lights are clearly horizontal coming from something fairly high in the sky, I called KEYE TV and they are sending out someone to investigate. Wish I had a video camera but I dont. Anyone else in Austin seeing this?
Summary: lights strobbing in NW Austin in circular pattern
